Remarks.

Macrostomum chongqingensis

has 
i
) the eyes lying near the brain, 
ii
) the adhesive plate situated at the hind end of the body, 
iii
) the ovaries that are paired, 
iv
) and the female gonopores that is situated in front of the male gonopores. These features clearly show that this new species belongs to 

Macrostomum

.

Remarks.
The species is undoubtedly a member of 

Macrostomum

, because it has 
i
) the eyes that lie in the brain, 
ii
) the adhesive plate in the hind end, 
iii
) the ovaries that are paired, and 
iv
) female gonopore that is situated in front of the male gonopore.
